Subclasses of ASysLogFormatter in de.systemagmbh.tools.logger.formatter
 class CSysCompatibilityLogFormatter
          The CSysCompatibilityFormatter builds a log output containing the date, the process id, the log level of the message, the part of the application that called the log method and the message itself.
 class CSysComplexLogFormatter
          The CSysComplexLogFormatter builds a log output containing the date, the process id, the log level of the message, the part of the application that called the log method and the message itself.

          The CSysComplexXMLLogFormatter builds log output in xml format.
 class CSysMessageFormatter
